edu.iastate.ansci.flip.extension

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iastate.ansci.flip.extension.Course

  • public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that defines the profile of a course
    1. id : identifier of the course. This is a unique value.
    2. nameCourse : Name of the course,
    3. section : Section of the course
    4. instructor : Instructor of the course
    5. comments : Any comment, optional
    6. word : A secret word used by students to request a Flip account at the Registration web page
    Author:
    Patricio Galdames
